r\n    刑。\r\n三、依刑事訴訟法第451條第1項聲請逕以簡易判決處刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c853%2c20221006%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉交簡,853,20221006,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉交簡","JNO":"853","JDATE":"20221006","JTITLE":"公共危險"}